type.description: The type of the event, always `response.image_gen_call.partial_image`.

sequence_number.description: The sequence number of the event that was emitted.

output_index.description: The index of the output item that was updated.

item_id.description: The ID of the tool call item that was updated.

partial_image_index.description: The index of the partial image that was emitted.

partial_image_b64.description: The base64-encoded partial image that was emitted.

size.description: The image size that was used.

quality.description: The image quality that was used.

background.description: The background setting that was used.

output_format.description: The output format that was used.

title: Response image generation call partial image event
description: A streaming event that indicated a partial image was emitted for an image generation call.
